\n\t4) tuck the corner of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bedsheet\" target=\"_blank\">bedsheet</a>s under the mattress<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tTucking the cuffs of his work gloves a bit, Doug wanted to make sure he would have a good grip on the object before picking it up. Equally important, no fingerprints should be left anywhere on site. Carefully picking up the thicker base, Doug lifted the glass sculpture with both hands. The art piece was heavier than he expected. With great caution, he inspected the piece in his hands from various angles. Because of the way the glass was coloured and the type of colouring used, the art sculpture caught the light differently at different angles.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169549302646/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827505/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p827505\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p846651/\">川普又作死了！自夸玩弄已婚女性曝光被狂喷</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p842304/\">当你要求女生娇小可人又文静的时候，她们遭受了什么</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p744721/\">四级成绩查询：英语四级提分133分励志逆袭经验</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p762386/\">有声美文：17件小事帮你轻松get更好的生活</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p842303/\">容易紧张？专业运动员教你如何应对！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p844731/\">听